title: What's The Next Collector Car You Must Buy Now? - AFTER/DRIVE
description: You might have missed the boat on an air-cooled 911, but there are plenty of other cars to get in on. Rob Sass, VP of Content at Hagerty, and Zac Moseley of Classic Car Club discuss which cars to watch, and which may never get off the ground.
tags: Collector car, classic cars, future classics
